Package: ConvQcENANDES
Title: Conventional Quality Control Tools for ENANDES Project
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Bruce Anthony", family = "Tumbaco Vega",
           email = "brucetumbac@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3558-2923"))
Description: Quality control for conventional meteorological data (precipitation and temperature) used in ENANDES+. 
    Includes format verification, logical ranges, Z-score (modified for precipitation), and Isolation Forest. 
    Provides plotting and export helpers. A built-in example dataset can be loaded with datos_ejemplo_convqc().
